CHANGES
=======

v0.6.0
------

Features:
* Add `haminfo db clone-from` command to copy database from one PostgreSQL
  instance to another using pg_dump/psql pipeline - enables syncing production
  data to development environments without hitting external APIs
* Update RepeaterBook API to use new token authentication with X-RB-App-Token
  header and REPEAT/1.0 User-Agent

Bug Fixes:
* Fix KeyError crash in /nearest endpoint when 'band' parameter not provided -
  Request.from_json now uses .get() for optional fields
* Fix container startup race condition - wait for db_upgrade to complete
* Remove noisy MQTT debug logs

Code Quality:
* Add required skills and context-mode instructions to AGENTS.md
* Add postgresql-client to Docker image for db clone command
* Clean up Request/WXRequest.from_json to use None instead of "None" string
  for optional field defaults

